6 (3) Each health facility or other provider of health care shall:
7 (a) Post in a publicly visible place in its[their] admission areas, outpatient areas,
8 and[, where applicable,] emergency areas, and on its website, as applicable,
9 that a consolidated,[an] itemized statement of health care services is required
10 to be furnished by the facility or provider whenever:
11 1. A patient, or patient's authorized representative, requests a statement
12 of charges or bill for health care services that have been provided to
