17 (b) Make available appropriate staff to provide a response to questions, and
18 resolve disputes, concerning any statement received under subsection (2) of
19 this section.
20 (4) The[ itemized] statement or statements furnished under subsection (2) of this
21 section[rendered] shall be the record maintained by the health facility or other
22 provider of health care that details the prices charged[charges made] for health
23 care services provided[rendered] to patients[ and shall indicate whether an
24 assignment of benefits has been obtained].
25 (5) [Each health facility shall designate and make available appropriate staff to provide,
26 upon patient request, an explanation of charges listed in the itemized statement.
27 (6) ]If a health facility or any other provider of health care knows of a discrepancy in
